description.narrative: UNICEF continues its active contribution on sector dialog to ensure RMNCAH IC guides partners. SWAP mechanism revision and HR WG revitalization are critical forums where UNICEF will continue engaged. Health management and governance capacity at the sub-national level, critical to the performance of health systems. Consequently, UNICEF has been supporting MoH at the district-level to improve evidence-based planning, health management capacity and accountability mechanisms. MoH is willing to institutionalize this approach into national planning guidelines and scale up to other priority districts. CHW platform expansion is contributing significantly for UHC in remote areas. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:01/01/2020
